cim:MeasurementValueSource.cim:IdentifiedObject.name: ICCP
cim:MeasurementValueSource.cim:IdentifiedObject.description: ICCP Measurement indicator. Change the pathName to set the name of the Local Control Center supplying the measurement data. Multiple MVSs may be created for multiple control centers, set the name to ICCP for all of them.

cim:MeasurementValueSource.cim:IdentifiedObject.name: CIM
cim:MeasurementValueSource.cim:IdentifiedObject.description: CIM database measurement indicator. The measurement data comes directly from entries in the model.

cim:MeasurementValueSource.cim:IdentifiedObject.name: PI Historian
cim:MeasurementValueSource.cim:IdentifiedObject.description: PI Measurement indicator. Change the pathName to set the name of the PI server.
